correctness.rationale: Extensive schema and factual issues. Key problems: (1) Schema violations and null/placeholder values in required fields: processParameters.pressure, plasmaPower, thicknessControl.growthPerCycle.values[].value, numberofCycles, nucleationPeriod, materialProperties.opticalProperties, electricalProperties, uniformity.variation, conformality.aspectRatio, roughness.value, filmDensity.value, and otherAspects.filmStability/reproducibility are set to None, which violates the schema types and the requirement of no empty/null values. ReactantSelection.carrierGas and purgingGas are filled with the placeholder string 'Not Found' rather than valid gases, despite being required by the schema. (2) Incorrect or untraceable values: deviceProperties.thresholdVoltage is set to −1.1 V, but the article reports V_ON (turn-on voltage), not V_TH; mapping V_ON to thresholdVoltage is incorrect. filmComposition.atomicRatio is given as '0.71:1:1' for [In, Ga, Zn], whereas the article only reports an In/Ga ratio of 0.71 with no Zn ratio; this is fabricated. processParameters.saturation is set to False without support in the text. supercycleDesign.subcycleSequence ['In','Ga','Zn'] and numberofSubcycles with None counts are ungrounded; the article notes controlling TEIn sub-cycles but gives no explicit sequence or counts. (3) Missing or incomplete extraction despite article details: The ALD temperature (200 °C) and substrate (SiO2/Si) are correct, and precursors/reactant (TEIn, In–Ga bimetallic, DEZn, O3) are correct. However, important reported device variants (Dev-A/B/C with T_CH = 5/10/15 nm) suggest multiple ALD processes differing in film thickness; only one process is represented. (4) Additional minor issues: Duplicate filmThickness fields, unspecified deliveryMethod, reactor info omitted, and pressure absent. Corrections needed: remove nulls or supply valid values; restrict atomicRatio to reported In:Ga = 0.71:1; omit thresholdVoltage unless V_TH is reported; remove unsupported saturation and subcycle details or provide grounded values; add separate process instances for 5, 10, and 15 nm films if possible; and populate carrier/purging gases and dosing/purge/flow parameters only if supported by the article or leave those sections out when optional (but schema currently requires them).

completeness.rationale: The extraction is largely incomplete and has multiple schema violations and factual issues. (1) Multiple processes missing: the article reports at least three distinct IGZO ALD channel thicknesses (Dev-A 5 nm, Dev-B 10 nm, Dev-C 15 nm) and also discusses a control with different GI thickness; only a single IGZO process (5 nm) is provided. The article also describes other ALD processes (Al2O3 spacer at 150 °C with TMA/H2O, Al2O3 PL and GI at 200 °C with TMA/O3, and AZO gate at 180 °C) that are not represented. (2) Schema non-compliance and nulls/placeholders: many required fields are null or placeholders, e.g., processParameters.pressure (quantityValue/unit/quantityKind = None), thicknessControl.growthPerCycle.values.value and numberofCycles = None, nucleationPeriod = None, uniformity.variation = None, conformality.aspectRatio = None, filmComposition.elementalConcentration.values = None, roughness and filmDensity = None, deviceProperties.fieldEffectMobility and onOffRatio = None, otherAspects.filmStability and reproducibility = None. Optional objects are included with null values (opticalProperties, electricalProperties, plasmaPower), which violates the schema typing. DosingTime/purgeTime/flowRates are required but provided as empty arrays without any compounds or QUDT-compliant values. CarrierGas and purgingGas are set to "Not Found" (not traceable data). SupercycleDesign.numberofSubcycles has counts set to None (should be omitted if unknown); only subcycleSequence is supported by the text. (3) Factual misalignments: deviceProperties.thresholdVoltage is populated with V_ON (−1.1 V) rather than a reported V_TH; filmComposition.atomicRatio is given as "0.71:1:1" whereas the article only reports an In/Ga ratio of 0.71 (no full In:Ga:Zn ratio). Saturation is set to false without evidence. (4) Missing measurable values available in the paper are not captured: the three IGZO film thicknesses (5/10/15 nm) as separate processes; SE-derived band gaps (≈3.11 and 3.14 eV) for IGZO test specimens; deposition temperatures for other ALD layers; and reported device structure is correct but other device metrics are not fully captured. To improve, add separate processes for Dev-A/B/C (and optionally Dev-AL and test specimens), remove null objects, supply only schema-compliant, traceable values (or omit optional fields), correct V_ON vs V_TH, avoid fabricated atomic ratios, and fill co-reactants per subcycle and any available parameters with proper QUDT units.
